<emphasis id="B9633869FFBEBB18823CBA27FDB92A53" box="[381,621,1087,1113]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="133">Pepumiri brasiliensis</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF86998AFFBEBB18813DBA27FCD42A50" author="Beier, M." box="[636,768,1087,1114]" pageId="4" pageNumber="133" pagination="468" refId="ref3769" refString="Beier, M. (1962) Orthoptera Tettigoniidae (Pseudophyllinae I). In: Mertens, R., Hennig, W. &amp; Wermuth, H. (Eds.), Das Tierreich. Vol. 73. Walter de Gruyter &amp; Co., Berlin, pp. 468." type="book chapter" year="1962">Beier, 1962</bibRefCitation>
